  "meal_prep_notes": "Sambar and cooked grain keep 3 days chilled. Reheat the sambar over medium-low heat for 5 minutes, thinning with hot water if it has thickened. Batch-cook the dal and grain separately so lunch portions can be assembled without overcooking the vegetables.",
